{"tid":559161,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點解棄用Kane   前阿仙奴青訓主管：佢太肥喇！","createTime":"2018-02-13T02:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T06:30:27.000Z","uid":4661,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b8f398f76c720c9ff02b9aa10170e7056c116725","tid":559161,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T02:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180212/large/1518450477_d330.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180212%2Flarge%2F1518450477_d330.jpg&h=310e1ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信好多球迷都知道，熱刺當紅球星哈利卡尼踢過阿仙奴青訓，但短短一年就被放棄，輾轉被熱刺收歸其下。對於當年為何棄用卡尼，前兵工廠青訓總監利姆巴迪（Liam Brady）就話：「他太肥了！」<br />\n<br />\n哈利卡尼目前在英超已射入101球，目前更在英超射手榜排第一，令阿仙奴大叫走寶。對於當年的真相，利姆巴迪說：「他當時有點肥胖，而且不強壯，但我們最終看錯了。就算熱刺收留他，都先要將他外借至低組別聯賽三至四次。但他的決心成就出精彩的職業生涯，而這是他應得的。」<br />\n<br />\n利姆巴迪又誇獎卡尼是世界第四人，他說：「美斯、C朗、利雲杜夫斯基之後，就到卡尼。數據證明一切，而卡尼現時只有24歲。」卡尼年僅九歲就被阿仙奴放走，如今名成利就，不是雲格又有否「揼心口」？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d66555c0cea09bf23deefe8e8abed0daccf15a","tid":559161,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T02:57:52.000Z","msg":"旁邊條友咩人"},{"pid":"9e7ea65650daf45fff0afbd54305fed0b0acdd50","tid":559161,"uid":110113,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"18d66555c0cea09bf23deefe8e8abed0daccf15a","tid":559161,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T02:57:52.000Z","msg":"旁邊條友咩人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:00:00.000Z","msg":"龍格堡"},{"pid":"fa1256cc8b8dfdd0549cc090f02e52758f065a3c","tid":559161,"uid":4957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:02:46.000Z","msg":"阿記 又贏一場！"},{"pid":"77f60ad78c77b98c48d27d3f80af17461059baa0","tid":559161,"ui